{"tid":989641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★高鐵西九龍站爆玻璃幕牆　碎片險墮內地離境大堂","createTime":"2019-01-21T04:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T06:10:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"725756038a64ba50c1d0b31af33bdc8fa3534e50","tid":989641,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/photo/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190121121730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190121121730&h=2eb5ff7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高鐵香港西九龍站發生爆玻璃事件。今早(21日)6時許，有東網讀者指西九龍站B2樓層一食店外，一塊約8呎乘5呎的玻璃幕牆突然爆裂，整塊玻璃呈網狀裂開，但未有碎開分離，職員發現後立即將附近圍起，因玻璃幕牆對落為B3樓層的候車大堂，屬內地範圍。職員亦通知內地人員將B3大堂局部圍封。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html&d=K1wQF2C3TgDSVQymfi9B2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1452a9f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f9a05d2531ce5f68fa8ece777389cae06084469c","tid":989641,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48d6acb1bb60b04644887e7852ee98a3d5656da","tid":989641,"uid":178875,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:25:12.000Z","msg":"一千億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf3e3d545c845b37b6564cec1200afdaa1b28c4",